OL,3,CLearner driver admits killing three
OL,4,Cfriends in crash near Dumfries
OL,6,FA learner driver has admitted killing
OL,7,Fthree of his friends in a crash near
OL,8,FDumfries.
OL,10,FJake Loy, 19, was speeding in his
OL,11,FHonda Civic when he lost control and
OL,12,Fcrashed into another car.
OL,14,FTyler Johnston, Ian Cannon, Finlay
OL,15,FJohns - all aged 16 and passengers in
OL,16,Fthe motor - never survived the crash
OL,17,Fon the A711 in Cargenbridge, on 16
OL,18,FMarch 2022.
