OL,3,CLearner driver admits killing three
OL,4,Cfriends in crash near Dumfries
OL,6,FA judge heard how Ian had posted a
OL,7,Fmessage in a group chat before the
OL,8,Fcrash that he was "scared" in the
OL,9,Fvehicle and that Loy was a "terrible
OL,10,Fdriver".
OL,12,FLoy - who only held a provisional
OL,13,Flicence at the time - appeared at the
OL,14,FHigh Court in Glasgow.
OL,16,FThe first offender pleaded guilty to a
OL,17,Fcharge of causing the death of the
OL,18,Fthree boys by dangerous driving.
