OL,6,FLoy, of , Dumfriesshire, had his bail
OL,7,Fcontinued by Lord Harrower pending
OL,8,Fsentencing in July.
OL,10,FThe teenager had initially been in his
OL,11,Fcar with Ian and Finlay before
OL,12,Ftravelling to Dumfries to pick-up
OL,13,FTyler.
OL,15,FStephen Jackson meantime was in the
OL,16,Farea around midnight driving back from
OL,17,Fa poker night with friends in his
OL,18,FHonda CR-V.
