OL,6,FHe was on the A711 at a slight bend
OL,7,Fwhen he recalled a black car suddenly
OL,8,F"coming towards him side on".
OL,10,FStephen desperately tried to avoid
OL,11,Fbeing hit, but Loy's Honda went
OL,12,F"straight into the front".
OL,14,FProsecutor Alex Prentice KC told how
OL,15,Fit was described as an "almighty
OL,16,Fimpact".
OL,18,FHe added: "The Crown position is that
OL,19,Fthe driver inexperience and excessive
OL,20,Fspeed were significant factors in the
OL,21,Floss of control of the vehicle."
