OL,6,FLoy's Honda split in two such was the
OL,7,Fforce of the collision.
OL,9,FOne experienced crash investigator
OL,10,Fsaid he had "never seen damage like
OL,11,Fthat to car". The actual speed Loy was
OL,12,Fdriving at is not known.
OL,14,FAn off-duty police officer initially
OL,15,Fstopped at the scene to help before
OL,16,Fmercy crews arrived.
OL,18,FThe three boys had already passed away
OL,19,Fas a result of their injuries.
