OL,6,FMr Prentice told how, hours after the
OL,7,Fcrash, a boy in the same Snapchat
OL,8,Fgroup as the teenagers saw a message
OL,9,FIan Cannon had written before the
OL,10,Ftragedy.
OL,12,FThe advocate depute: "He was saying
OL,13,Fthat he was scared because Jake Loy
OL,14,Fwas swerving all over the place, that
OL,15,Fhe was a terrible driver and he was
OL,16,Fflooring it.
OL,18,F"It is not possible to pinpoint the
OL,19,Fprecise point in the journey the
OL,20,Fmessage was sent."
