OL,6,FThe court heard Stephen Jackson was
OL,7,Falso badly hurt.
OL,9,FHe suffered a fractured kneecap and
OL,10,Fhand as well as bruising.
OL,12,FHe is scarred for life and remains
OL,13,Faffected by what happened including
OL,14,Fstruggling to play with his child and
OL,15,Fsports he took part in.
OL,17,FStephen may end up getting arthritis
OL,18,Fin his knee. He has also received
OL,19,Fpsychological treatment.
