OL,6,FThe charge Loy pleaded guilty to also
OL,7,Fstated he seriously injured the man
OL,8,Fand two of his passengers.
OL,10,FThe teenager also need hospital
OL,11,Ftreatment after the crash.
OL,13,FIn June 2022, he went on to attend
OL,14,Fwith his lawyer at a local police
OL,15,Fstation and claimed he "did not know"
OL,16,Fthe driver at the time of the crash.
OL,18,FEmotional family and friends of the
OL,19,Fthree victims packed the courtroom
OL,20,Ftoday.
