OL,6,FMr Prentice told how all three had
OL,7,Fattended Moffat Academy.
OL,9,FFinlay was studying for his highers,
OL,10,FTyler had gone on to college in
OL,11,FDumfries while Ian had stayed in
OL,12,FGlasgow after leaving school, but had
OL,13,Freturned to live with his mum and
OL,14,Fsister.
OL,16,FDonald Findlay KC, defending, later
OL,17,Ftold the hearing that Loy had "no
OL,18,Frecollection" of the crash.
